c=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03386e63c819da1597da37ef908c1a00efb67d1a","tid":2016121,"uid":51540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:10:32.000Z","msg":"一飲全日就會周身唔聚財勁唔舒服<br />\n飲完一樣係眼訓但偏偏想訓都訓唔到"},{"pid":"056560191c209f28406c096ec2eb2dd2e0e0b79a","tid":2016121,"uid":157107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身體對Caffeine會build up <del>intolerance</del> <br />\n想keep住有效要每個月停飲大約一星期</blockquote><br />\nTolerance"},{"pid":"e0bab95f5c0f826f5dc9e358e1216680061f20b5","tid":2016121,"uid":251119,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"55b8a155cfe2a93b3f1ee5e2ef7ee776d6fb4de4","tid":2016121,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"062dbb7c99c22e199f1a64aff2337fdfc02e0e49","tid":2016121,"uid":62841,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:25:58.000Z","msg":"咖啡因要喺精神嘅時候攝取先有用<br />\n自己google下個原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋用得多會失效"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:01:08.000Z","msg":"講真我google過都唔明點解精神時攝取先有用<br />\n介唔介意講多d？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"人會感到攰係因為身體會產生一種神經傳導物質（唔記得係乜）<br />\n呢舊野一旦combine左落去神經上既receptor到 人就會feel到攰<br />\n而咖啡因既作用就係搶先一步combine左落去啲receptor先<br />\n咁個種神經傳導物質就combine唔到落receptor <br />\n從而人就feel唔到攰<br />\n<br />\n點解要清醒個陣飲咖啡<br />\n就係因為當你feel到攰個陣 即係代表啲神經傳導物質已經combine哂落receptor到<br />\n呢個時候你再飲幾多咖啡都冇用 因為咖啡因已經冇位比佢combine<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個時候你係應該小睡一陣先（個人經驗15mins都夠）<br />\n等身體清空哂個啲神經傳導物質先 咁樣啲咖啡因先有位入<br />\n<br />\n利申：憑記憶講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有錯勿屌"},{"pid":"c011de932f0a6b228a083fd9054984529e962eb4","tid":2016121,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9ab97017becbcefdeca46c2b08d8e83e6367e80","tid":2016121,"uid":302638,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:40:35.000Z","msg":"Caffeine嘅原理係霸住啲adenosine receptor唔比你有睡意 但係個腦見啲receptor比人用左就會整多啲receptor出嚟<br />\n最後你一唔用caffeine 啲多左嘅receptor反而會令多啲adenosine有作用 即係瞓得仲快<br />\n呢啲嘢都係唔好太依賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"咁嘅話，我朝早狂飲咖啡，夜晚就可以瞓快啲？<br />\n屌我試吓先，已經失眠幾個月，每晚四點先瞓着，七點又起身返工，搭車放工先恰一陣，返到屋企又瞓唔著"},{"pid":"2c7d9b7a405677d256a2ecdde5513428b4aac541","tid":2016121,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19fdaa8cbf10bc45203bb20720a81c9ce83dba89","tid":2016121,"uid":35336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:24:47.000Z","msg":"唔飲會頭痛<br />\n差唔多要一日兩杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"早午晚<br />\n起碼3杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e349d883311c4e24d611e1f052ab7f8706cab5","tid":2016121,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"打咖啡因針囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452224ab99e1e96c00e2070880f1eaee2fa20063","tid":2016121,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:15:50.000Z","msg":"我飲/食咗有咖啡因嘅嘢會完全瞓唔到<br />\n床上眼光光起碼三幾個鐘<br />\n茶 咖啡 汽水 朱古力"},{"pid":"9eb2658b920e00a5375034f58a634b146c90b0fb","tid":2016121,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0bab95f5c0f826f5dc9e358e1216680061f20b5","tid":2016121,"uid":251119,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"55b8a155cfe2a93b3f1ee5e2ef7ee776d6fb4de4","tid":2016121,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"062dbb7c99c22e199f1a64aff2337fdfc02e0e49","tid":2016121,"uid":62841,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:25:58.000Z","msg":"咖啡因要喺精神嘅時候攝取先有用<br />\n自己google下個原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋用得多會失效"},"citedBy":2,"reply