y":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:18:06.000Z","msg":"而喝咖啡之所以能達到提神的效果，主要是因為咖啡因與腺苷有相似的解構，而且咖啡因是腺苷的拮抗劑 (antagonist)，會阻礙腺苷與其接受器的結合，影響睡眠驅力的累積，因而可以達到提神的效果。<br />\n<br />\n本身攰嘅話啲receptor已經被occupy"},{"pid":"e84416d4b1a161ef509a20b78e5eb423943f7dcd","tid":2016121,"uid":165184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"累&gt;飲咖啡&gt;仲想訓&gt;訓15-30分鐘&gt;精神過何君妖"},{"pid":"5c573ecd3f42512ab1357282a7e9675c79d5ee76","tid":2016121,"uid":236860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:19:40.000Z","msg":"我由以前飲完眼瞓飲到飲完好精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a625658427ed1941f468cc912fc3f84b6ab3cd","tid":2016121,"uid":6106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"唔知邊到睇過話飲完咖啡訓番20分鐘個人就會開始醒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以飲完咖啡應該要小睡效果先好"},{"pid":"37f23f79b98a00132caf7608fbadd0a2f16bdb29","tid":2016121,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"我都想呀屌 有時自己食dinner 忍唔到口飲杯奶茶果晚實訓唔到<br />\nlunch飲就好少少 但都會有影響"},{"pid":"8a84e5fcb61502275151af9da6435e7692f8979e","tid":2016121,"uid":100817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"連茶飲多一杯都會頭痛"},{"pid":"d99ac38d9e0fc61ca5df036013dbe5c7dd04a42d","tid":2016121,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c011de932f0a6b228a083fd9054984529e962eb4","tid":2016121,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9ab97017becbcefdeca46c2b08d8e83e6367e80","tid":2016121,"uid":302638,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:40:35.000Z","msg":"Caffeine嘅原理係霸住啲adenosine receptor唔比你有睡意 但係個腦見啲receptor比人用左就會整多啲receptor出嚟<br />\n最後你一唔用caffeine 啲多左嘅receptor反而會令多啲adenosine有作用 即係瞓得仲快<br />\n呢啲嘢都係唔好太依賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"咁嘅話，我朝早狂飲咖啡，夜晚就可以瞓快啲？<br />\n屌我試吓先，已經失眠幾個月，每晚四點先瞓着，七點又起身返工，搭車放工先恰一陣，返到屋企又瞓唔著"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"咪話左唔好依賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真答 先唔講啲多左嘅receptor過一兩個禮拜就會散曬 其實你唔會知飲幾多咖啡先會啱啱好 咁玩法分分鐘成日瞓唔着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用幾個禮拜嘅失眠換三四日嘅瞓得着 仲要只係瞓得着 唔係瞓得好 你話值唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n失眠都係搵醫生睇睇佢好"},{"pid":"f88b82c2e701c372ada577bdbccb1bd74fe3c87c","tid":2016121,"uid":81533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:24:18.000Z","msg":"朝早飲杯茶就會精神到瞓唔著，飲濃小小仲會手震......"},{"pid":"a30e7f09bfb5cc362d59212a9f1ca59636a8210c","tid":2016121,"uid":289703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:32:06.000Z","msg":"每日3至6 shot"},{"pid":"89d9b79d183bd80215a1cf7c86fe2580a050a5f3","tid":2016121,"uid":96218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:34:08.000Z","msg":"冇飲一個禮拜之後第一啖嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個心光速咁跳"},{"pid":"abed192e97a2a47bd1470af7b3b9f5ae836c74df","tid":2016121,"uid":42434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:34:14.000Z","msg":"由細到大都無有效過 <br />\n飲咖啡只係當一般野飲"},{"pid":"a2e9a555caebd9cbb312a0a57a2c4c02f8083103","tid":2016121,"uid":234220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:34:16.000Z","msg":"食完飯都無睡意 貪新鮮飲完新出個支咖啡可樂, 依家眼瞓到想到死....."},{"pid":"6de678f2d9837c2457b47c4916141326a65e6d39","tid":2016121,"uid":172202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:34:38.000Z","msg":"以前飲會好似興奮劑咁 好多野講好癲咁樣 依家飲只係當安慰劑 有時甚至覺得更眼訓"},{"pid":"b4d5502090e23224d064d360042045d53289c4b1","tid":2016121,"uid":239486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:38:20.000Z","msg":"有一晚飲咗八杯齋啡，都